{"tid":1388453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班撚樣咪撚再講陪審員呀！！！","createTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T02:14:58.000Z","uid":1251,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4785054a73560b63ce2bb5637a56f5dc788ad01","tid":1388453,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你知唔知你可能害到義士呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有心既唔駛你講都自然會作出正確決定<br />\n冇心既你講乜佢都唔聽架啦<br />\n<br />\n你地咁撚樣高調講<br />\n其實係俾緊子彈DOJ<br />\n萬一真係去到高院義士贏左</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">DOJ可以話陪審員有可能受到網上人士影響作出非獨立決定而推翻裁決<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班義士到時就俾你地累死！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b36ac8d955fe85e02d89a56d4a933bb8312ec862","tid":1388453,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8937184b7cc15cda899dc9e4f441489981e4fae","tid":1388453,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ef86f062b373e47dc0373d249ce6d0fdbe5e84","tid":1388453,"uid":6843,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26ccdcfc4a6cbb2185822f42e535d8c7039bbaf3","tid":1388453,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6288220c8beaf2a6fd3709b373b2b5b75c131cf","